    <!-- About Content -->
    <section class="py-16">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-center text-blue-600">About News in Blues</h2>
            <div class="bg-white shadow-md rounded-lg p-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                <p class="mb-4">Welcome to News in Blues, your trusted source for global news and insights. We are committed to delivering accurate, timely, and comprehensive news coverage to keep you informed about the world around you.</p>
                
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-blue-600">Our Mission</h3>
                <p class="mb-4">At News in Blues, our mission is to empower our readers with knowledge and understanding. We believe that well-informed citizens are the foundation of a thriving society, and we strive to provide the information you need to engage with the world confidently.</p>
                
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-blue-600">What We Offer</h3>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
                    <li>Comprehensive coverage of global and local news</li>
                    <li>In-depth analysis and expert opinions</li>
                    <li>Diverse perspectives on current events</li>
                    <li>Timely updates on breaking news</li>
                    <li>User-friendly interface for easy navigation</li>
                </ul>
                
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2 text-blue-600">Our Values</h3>
                <p class="mb-4">We are guided by the principles of journalistic integrity, impartiality, and transparency. Our team of experienced journalists and editors work tirelessly to ensure that the news we deliver is accurate, balanced, and free from bias.</p>
                
                <p>Thank you for choosing News in Blues as your go-to news source. We're committed to keeping you informed and inspired, one story at a time.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

